On 4 Sep 95, at 12:00, Luca Carminati collapsed under the weight of:

> is there anyone who can tell me what the #WA_PointerDelay tag is for?

 It causes the changing of the pointer to a busy pointer to be 
delayed for a short time, thus preventing short flashes of the busy 
pointer.



