Date: Sun, 11 Oct 1998 19:02:22 +0200 (CEST)
From: Gustav Gnosspelius <gosweede@lindesign.se>
Subject: Changing text style


 I was very surprised to see that there are no "simple" command to change
the font-style in Amigamode (bold/italic/underlined). Do I really have to
