@NODE "Mail_78" "Re: Changing text style"
          Paris Sun, 11 Oct 1998 22:51:20 +0200 (MET DST)
          Paris Sun, 11 Oct 1998 22:51:14 +0200 (MET DST)
From: Gigandet Jean-Marc <HURRICAN@wanadoo.fr>
Date: Sun, 11 Oct 1998 22:51:35 +0100
Subject: Re: Changing text style

That's the LoadFont job !

Syntax : LoadFont IntuiFont#,Fontname.font$,Y size [,style]

Here are the style parameters. Note that they can be combined.

#underlined=1
#bold=2
#italic=4
#extended=8
#Colour=64 


-- 
