> that are *not* described in the manuals e.g. Clearmenustrip,
> WindowTags, DetachGTList, GTSetHighlight and many others?

You might try and find a program called ViewDefLibs.bb2.  This 
program goes through all your libs and lists all the commands 
available.  If you have the blitzcd have a look around in the bum 
files, it`s in there somewhere.  If not, search about in Aminet in 
dev/Basic.

Bye
Steven



