@NODE "Mail_94" "Re: Commands"
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Tue, 27 Oct 1998 14:48:26 +0000
From: "Nick Chapman" <scillo@geocities.com>
Subject: Re: Commands
Date: Tue, 27 Oct 1998 14:39:53 -0000
	charset="iso-8859-1"
Encoding: 8bit

There isn't anything as handy as this at the moment. The aim of my WIP
manual is to document all the relevant commands. The format is on a "how to"
basis, hence only the best way of doing something is documented. That isn't
some dictatorial assertion as to what is "best", but, for example, I won't
bother documenting the "Req" library when "Reqtools" is so much better.

Nick / Skillo

