DONT get Blitz CD if you already have BSS.  The cd is only 
35megs full and basically only contains bb2.1, the manual as text 
files, all the BUMS, and some stuff from Aminet.  A huge 
dissapointment for a seasoned Blitzer such as myself.  I see that 
