Look at example called BlitzIdentify (Aminet/dev/basic) - here you can
find an example of using identify.library in Blitz. This usefull
library is used to get near all information about your amiga - disks,
devices - everything. Library is working only on 2.0+ machines and
could use locale to output information. Very interesting example. My
eTeacher (WWW on SIG) is using identify.library too ;-)

