On Wed, Oct 14, 1998 at 12:31:58AM -0600, Andrew Drays said:
> ok.. I've been getting a lot of stuff done.. and having fun doing it..
> 
> my latest dilemma.. .. I'm got stuff going tinto a listview.. and it's
> constantly haivng input come in.. from IRC.. how do I have my listview stick
> with scolling what's on the bottom instead of the TOP? so as input comes in..
> it keeps going down.. sntead of having to keep moving the scroll bar?!? 

Try setting GT_TOP or whatever it is. This sets the top of the visible
listview. Just increment it by the number of lines added by the
logging program, and you will stay at the bottom. 

