> used to be on www.amiga.com, but I've just looked and they don't 
> appear to be there any more.

Autodocs and RKMS are good placed to look for this stuff but
all Blitz users will have a list of AmigaOS tags and constants anyway.
Blitz comes with an "AmiIncludes" drawer which contains all the
Amiga Includes that are needed to use Blitz' OS functions.

You can find the #GTLV_ tags in AmiIncludes/libraries/gadtools.bb2

Line 218 is you need more help ;)

Cheers,

