Hello Wright

Somewhere  Wright J.A wrote:
> =

> arggghhhhh...... someone plz help  8)
> =


Fear no more! El NutHole is here!

I made this generic source so that it can be quickly used in any code...

Cya...
-- =

Best Regards,
Rui Carvalho =ABgRiM=BB

*=ABBlitz Basic Source Code Site=BB*
#Http://ip.pt/~ip234558 - Last Update: 19.09.98#
#Fruit Cake Mailing List - fruitcake-subscribe@egroups.com#

--BOUNDARY.2015919528.2
Content-Disposition: attachment; filename="GTList.BB2"

; GTLIST PROCEDURE
; Made by gRiM

WBStartup
WbToScreen 0

NEWTYPE .list
numero.w
n$
End NEWTYPE


Dim List num.list(20)

For a=1 To 20
If AddItem(num())
num()\n=Str$(Int(Rnd(99)+1))
EndIf
Next

GTListView 0,0,10,10,70,60,"",$4,num()

Window 0,0,0,640,200,$100a,"",2,1
AttachGTList 0,0

Repeat

Select Event
  Case $200
    End
  Case $40
    cli=EventCode
    WLocate 10,80:NPrint cli
End Select

Forever





--BOUNDARY.2015919528.2--




