Subject: Re: GTstring activate

Hi Andrew,

On 28-Oct-98, Andrew Drays wrote:
> I know activatesting will work for standard stings.. but I'm looking for a
> similar command or gttag for GTstring..

The same command works for a GTstring gadget.

When in doubt, I always try just adding "GT" in front of the command.  If that
won't tokenise, I try using the non-GT version of the command.  Usually one or
the other will work.  Sometimes both  ;) 

