> heya.. I need help.. I'm trying to create a style of window that can have
text
> scroll down.. except I'm not sure how I can handle this via Gadtools.. I've
> attempted a gttext style window.. but it don't work right.. it only does one
> line at a time, although it does correct it and display it nice.. it doesn't
> quit handle all the text and doesn't do multiple lines.. I was wondering if
> anyone could clue me in another way to handle this.. 

I have an example on my web page for making a text viewer in a window.  It
uses a GTlistview gadget for the display, so you can scroll up and down with
the arrows or the slider bar.  Also word wraps and can use any font and any
reasonable size of window.  Maybe this would be helpful to you.

