@NODE "Mail_245" "Re: HELP! Most wanted Blitz Libs."
 for blitz-list@netsoc.ucd.ie; Thu, 15 Oct 1998 12:02:06 +0000
From: Paul Burkey <burkey@bigfoot.com>
Date: Thu, 15 Oct 1998 12:53:22 +0000
Subject: Re: HELP! Most wanted Blitz Libs.
