>Hello everybody

>same as the subject: how can i know if a window was opened or not?
>i have no idea, i'm a beginner in OS and GUI

Hi Christian,

I don't know if this can fit you but when I open a window, I set a variab=
le to
1, and when I close it, I reset the variable to 0. This way I know if the=

window is opened just by checking the variable.

See you...




