Hey man,

flooding people with hatemail, Amigabashers or not, is a very silly =
thing to do. Do not do it. As for websites, try www.amiga.de for the =
official homepage of our fave computer. Games news is best dealt with by =
www.amigaflame.co.uk . Both of these sites have links to others. Try the =
homepages of the people on this list, they tend to be full of useful =
stuff. I may as well get a plug in for the Skillo Website as well. =
www.bomb.demon.co.uk

Nick
