--BOUNDARY.1749632952.6
Encoding: quoted-printable


    Hi Blitzers,

    I've attached to this mail the exec version of my new screen mode
preference program. It's done 100% which the NewCommandSet (so you can bu=
ild
real apps wit it, it's no joke :-).

    It brings:

    + Fully gadtools font sensitive interface (it's better no ?)
    + Some bugs fixed against the old C=3D version

    It lacks localization support, and some other stuffs (menus aren't
working...). If anybody is interrested to finish it, say me.
 =

    My goal was to rewrite all the pref proggy, but I've no more time to =
do it
(The harder is done, as it's mostly only the interface which change betwe=
en
all the pref proggy...)

    bYe,

                        Fred.

