Encoding: quoted-printable


    Blitzers,

    Thanks for trying the NCS V1.40. Most of you have problem with the
NLibs.res file. The solution would be to do a Rom 3.1 version of the
Amigalibs.res file so this NLibs.res would be only for Specific NCS comma=
nds.

    I've included the source file of NLibs.res, so remove useless stuffs =
and
recompile it...

    Good luck (Its not so hard =3D:-) !

                        Fred.

