    In fact, if your read my first e-mail attentionnaly, you will see tha=
t the
project I propose is a so called 'Macro compiler'. I've named it HIGH Lev=
el
langage. You idea is in fact very good. I've written my own ASM to prove =
to me
that I was able to do it. And to be sure that I can writte a PPC ASM with=
out
difficulties. Don't forget than PPC ASM are simpler to do because it has =
much
less instructions (RISC =3D Reduced Instruction Set Cpu). PPC is RISC. 68=
000 is
CISC (Complex Instruction....).
