You have to use a bigger bitmap (i.e. 640x256). Then just
use the 

DISPLAYBITMAP bitmapnumber,x,y 

command the get some smooth scrolling.

For some example whats possible in BB2 if ya head for a
mario styled game then check out this 32kb archieve

