okay I just did and it was just over 9k difference. So for the sake of
6k I agree that is it bigger but once you've written your own
version of ASLFileRequest$ using OS functions with taglists
and such you'd end up with something that is only a little bit
smaller. This is why it's no worth worrying about such a tiny lib.

